- No spec, no code.
- Always create/update: SPEC + tests + docs per change.
- Keep changes small and reviewable.
- Validate all inputs. Never trust client input.
- Centralized error handling with typed error codes.
- All network calls: timeout + safe retries.
- No secrets in repo. Use env vars.
- Add logging with correlation IDs for every request.
- Add basic rate limiting and abuse prevention for AI endpoints.
- Every DB change must have migration and rollback.
- Privacy-by-design: minimize data; plan export/delete.
- Safety-by-design for training/nutrition advice (red flags -> recommend professional).
